item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Winter Ice:

mabe because somone or you is banned from your ip or it is because your using AOL

That is correct.

Your ISP doesn’t give you a new IP every time you connect, often you’ll find your IP has been used at least 10 times before, or even more on AOL, as often the problems come from AOL users.

On a side note, it says I’ve been banned on a few of my favourite sites before.
